==Comment Feature
As a guest I should be able to post a comment
As a user I should be able to post a comment
As guest or user my comment needs to be approved before being displayed
Requires a name, email address, comment body, captcha

Given I have posted a comment
My email address should be added to the notification email list

==Notification of New Articles Feature
Given i put my email address in the notification sign up form
I should be able to get a notification of posts
"Notify me of new Posts"

==Classes Feature
Read only list of posted classes
When the user clicks on a class, it requires a password
Class should only be 1 video